data.description: Discover your dream home in this exquisite three-story single-family residence, nestled within a highly coveted community where homes rarely become available. Boasting an immaculate clean aesthetic, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere, accentuated by a 2 story foyer and a two-directional staircase that adds a touch of architectural elegance. The main level beckons you to unwind in front of the cozy fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxing evenings. For those seeking ultimate relaxation, a luxurious soaking tub awaits in one of the two full baths. The main level features a deck off kitchen, ideal for al fresco dining and enjoying scenic views of the lush backyard. Storage enthusiasts will delight in the multitude of closets throughout the home, ensuring that you have room for all your belongings. The pinnacle of organization can be found in the enormous L-shaped master walk-in closet. This home is equipped with modern amenities, including an available total home water filtration system, providing pure and clean water for your family's needs. The spacious unfinished fully studded basement holds immense potential for customization, with the opportunity to add up to three additional rooms and two more baths, allowing you to tailor the space to your unique desires. With five bedrooms and a convenient half bath, there's no shortage of space for your family and guests. The community itself is closely monitored by a hired officer, ensuring a safe and secure environment for all residents. Don't miss your chance to own a meticulously maintained, three-story single-family home that combines comfort, style, and the potential for customization. This rare opportunity won't last long.
